title: GDP of New Brunswick , Canada 2000 to 2018
yAxis: GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars, containing a total of 19 data points.
Overall GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2001 and 2002.
The highest GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars, of value 30446.6 was reached at Year 2018
Minimum GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars about 25058.0 was reached at Year 2000
